					"type": 23,
					"value": "Idle AD conversation between bandits who occupy hag survivors building when the hag is not in the city.\r\n\r\nThe bandits are in hiding from the steel watch after a job gone wrong. When not blaming each other, they decide to kill anyone who sets foot in this building."
